      <title>美光股价下跌，因前景未达到预期上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/micron-falls-as-outlook-fails-to-meet-high-end-of-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美光的预测令那些希望从人工智能热潮中获得更多回报的投资者感到失望。彭博情报的 Mandeep Singh 分析了这一预测以及美光在人工智能以外的传统市场。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/micron-falls-as-outlook-fails-to-meet-high-end-of-estimates</guid>
