    <item>
      <title>BTV 嘉宾出席周日法国大选第一轮投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/btv-guests-ahead-of-french-elections-1st-round-sunday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国立法选举首轮将于 6 月 30 日星期日举行。竞选活动于周五法国时间午夜/美国东部时间 18:00 结束。马克龙总统在欧洲选举中落败后突然宣布提前举行选举，令所有人措手不及，竞选活动仅持续了不到三周。
在第一轮竞选的最后一天，我们回顾了彭博电视台一些嘉宾自那时以来的言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/btv-guests-ahead-of-french-elections-1st-round-sunday</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若欧洲央行降低法国债券收益率，德国可能表示反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 表示，如果法国立法选举引发该国政府债券的危险抛售，欧洲央行的干预可能是非法的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士扩大与美国银行数据共享 打击逃税行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/swiss-widen-bank-data-sharing-with-us-in-tax-dodging-clampdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士和美国已加强银行信息的自动交换，这使得美国公民更难以阻止自己的账户数据落入美国税务机关的手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/swiss-widen-bank-data-sharing-with-us-in-tax-dodging-clampdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:16:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院限制 SEC 内部法官审理欺诈案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-curbs-sec-s-use-of-in-house-judges-in-fraud-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院限制了美国证券交易委员会向内部法官提出申诉的能力，称当该机构寻求经济处罚时，被告有宪法权利向联邦陪审团陈述案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-curbs-sec-s-use-of-in-house-judges-in-fraud-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西称美洲诈骗案目标已逃离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/brazil-police-search-home-of-americanas-directors-over-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西联邦警察进行了迄今为止最大规模的行动，对美洲零售商 SA 大规模欺诈案的责任人进行了惩罚，并在里约热内卢签发了逮捕令和搜查令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/brazil-police-search-home-of-americanas-directors-over-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受阴雨天气影响，可可价格将遭遇两年来最长的跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/cocoa-heads-for-longest-decline-in-two-years-on-good-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场关注点转向有利于西非主要种植区的作物生长的有利天气，纽约可可期货遭遇了两年来最长的连续下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/cocoa-heads-for-longest-decline-in-two-years-on-good-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
